Nawal Al Zoghbi starred in winter
01 Nov 2019, 11:28 by Riham Kadri
Riham Kadry published the artist Nawal Al Zoghbi through her personal page on the social networking site and the exchange of photos and videos "Instagram" a new picture of her. Nawal appeared with a winter look with a gray jacket and a colorful keffiyeh, and a gentle and neat makeup in light brown of lipstick and painted eyebrows with her blond hair color, which gave her a superb beauty.
